title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 24 2022
description:
Ann Coulter joins Buck to celebrate the overturning of Roe v. Wade and the GOP senators who buckled on the gun control bill. Biden denounces violence in response to Roe decision, but AOC screams, "Take to the streets!" Larry Kudlow on how the Biden Regime is destroying the economy, predicts stagflation. Don't sleep on yesterday's big gun ruling. Democrats always make emotional, not legal, arguments. Biden, Eric Adams respond to SCOTUS gun decision.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
